      "anchor_concept_id": "spine_mathematics_l3_second_order_linear_odes",
      "content": {
        "title": "Characteristic Equation",
        "definition": "For ay″ + by′ + cy = 0, substitute y = e^{rx} to obtain ar² + br + c = 0 whose roots determine the solution form.",
        "summary": "The characteristic polynomial reduces second-order ODEs to algebraic root-finding."
      },
