      "content": {
        "title": "Complex Conjugate Roots",
        "definition": "When r = α ± βi, solution y = e^{αx}(C₁ cos βx + C₂ sin βx) exhibits oscillation modulated by exponential envelope.",
        "summary": "Complex roots model damped or undamped oscillations in mechanical and electrical systems."
      },
