      "content": {
        "title": "Real Distinct Roots",
        "definition": "When r₁ ≠ r₂ are real, general solution y = C₁e^{r₁x} + C₂e^{r₂x}.",
        "summary": "Real distinct roots produce exponential modes without oscillation."
